  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "c928e0a096903df0079f7e059e77f7150acc6555fec473e32c000344cb1c255a": "With respect, my Queen, were it not for [?] here, I would have died at the hands of the Emissaries. I believe he has earned our trust.",
    "c61e3c5c6254896392ca9b292ebc47da8fe2e68bb55843e692e6727ebc406112": "With respect, my Queen, were it not for [?] here, I would have died at the hands of the Emissaries. I believe she has earned our trust.",
    "e82c3c6476f07c2984454747e5372134c2c36ce235aa32527a4c79601155291a": "With respect, my Queen, were it not for [?] here, I would have died at the hands of the Emissaries. I believe they have earned our trust.",
    "7fe390d588098bbd431eeea0ab2da3223ffaf0b540384dcef8cd78054555a1e8": "Thank you, my Queen. Come, [?], let us meet with this dwarf in the market.",
    "3c5734964f1143b0fcf02c2914f6a33f7b2187c4b20cd55cf128e23973a2c74c": "Good luck, [?]. May the sun light your way.",
    "6cd8b35e793c7c4953912d2c483c484ebae40c0e9d34bc4daf87e216bda78e80": "[?]! Thank Ralos you're here!",
    "6db4b726967d4678f3fc62d57b64b59320a4575e867ac808fa1825494fbc14bb": "[?], you must go to the Crypt of Tonali and help with the defence. It's beneath the large temple south east of here."
